{"tid":1588091,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"GTA-FIVEM SERVER PROMOTION 卷圈之城","createTime":"2019-09-22T16:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T16:23:01.000Z","uid":68031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"50acc38b6440bdb814ad0e9f8380f6b59fae03b0","tid":1588091,"uid":68031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:15:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cjerBDq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcjerBDq.png&h=83474efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>城市名: 光圈之城 </strong></span></ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uGx1qnj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuGx1qnj.gif&h=95fd147e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">大家好!我係宣傳部MIC!</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">IP: 139.99.68.152:30120</span></strong><br />\n(可以在FIVEM內 F8 輸入 connect 139.99.68.152:30120 直接進入)<br />\nFIVEM 就不多說了, 就是一個GTA 5 聯機軟件, 插入多個由服主加入的車MOD及遊戲文件!<br />\n光圈之城背景: 由一班經多個伺服器洗禮過後的玩家,確定自己對RP的熱愛.聚首於光圈之城! 扮演自己想成為的角色! 本伺服主要以廣東話溝通!多謝支持!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> (服內好多愛車之人) 一星期更新5至10架車種上架(未上架有過百種)</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/617343255683661829/623300243181666308/6edc70-4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F617343255683661829%2F623300243181666308%2F6edc70-4.png&h=cb52c3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/617343255683661829/624607553128628225/1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F617343255683661829%2F624607553128628225%2F1.png&h=2b5e1557&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/617343255683661829/625032223619416065/1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F617343255683661829%2F625032223619416065%2F1.png&h=e5188ca9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/617343255683661829/625032337935302688/1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F617343255683661829%2F625032337935302688%2F1.png&h=fdae5f58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/624242602044293161/625212789861908501/239fc9-46871186022_968f3823b4_o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F624242602044293161%2F625212789861908501%2F239fc9-46871186022_968f3823b4_o.png&h=ce7cdea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">特別娛樂 (有老闆,職位):</span></strong></ins><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>夜店-凱撒皇宮</strong></span><br />\n給予大家飲下酒!做盡另一個自己!在內發生既任何事,都非常安全!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J46ieVA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ46ieVA.png&h=7f5118f7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aAsA1wV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaAsA1wV.gif&h=890d3b91&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">賭場-冒險樂園</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0f2tB8T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0f2tB8T.png&h=45c03c70&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pAtP52e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpAtP52e.png&h=ebb32ff5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U2TTOft.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU2TTOft.png&h=7366b5ee&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H7CdOft.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH7CdOft.png&h=efeb05a5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fowx3OP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFowx3OP.png&h=7b21d20c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0EjJOQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0EjJOQ.png&h=d71dcb0c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YKZvQtR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKZvQtR.png&h=d77b07da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktPr8fw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktPr8fw.png&h=f9760d45&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>租船出海釣魚</strong></span><br />\n看看海!~釣下魚,傾下心,釣下釣下,釣到金!?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZL4DeVs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZL4DeVs.png&h=9fcf833d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">部份職位:</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>售車及修車基地 - 雨宮車房</strong></span><br />\n設備齊全!擁有全市車種!修改多進口車輛技術!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eFXxjnc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeFXxjnc.png&h=4fa3e567&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong>的士-勃勃的士</strong></span><br />\n係你最吾方便既時候出現!安全抵達目的地!使命!必達!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hrcEJLj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhrcEJLj.gif&h=5186bd1c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong>警察警徵</strong></span></span><br />\n少廢話,打擊城內罪犯!確保守法城內市民安全!安全居住光圈之內!<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/617362847172788228/625244460766330880/gtafivempolice.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F617362847172788228%2F625244460766330880%2Fgtafivempolice.png&h=5e93a473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>醫管局</strong></span></span><br />\n光圈之城-醫管局之宗旨是&quot;不忘初心 牢記使命&quot; <br />\n你的生命守護神,藍白色情人!<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/617362847172788228/625357220179345428/image0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F617362847172788228%2F625357220179345428%2Fimage0.png&h=b3c3f39b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/617046477881081887/620230994523324426/amb_gta.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F617046477881081887%2F620230994523324426%2Famb_gta.png&h=822bc0df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/605777207171874855/623945785867763714/123.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F605777207171874855%2F623945785867763714%2F123.png&h=23367a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>黑幫 - 洪門</strong></span><br />\n為達到目的,用盡所有方法!擁有最好的計劃,團隊性!光城唯我天下!<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/607993125948096512/625361845171257374/-2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F607993125948096512%2F625361845171257374%2F-2.gif&h=e7dac908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/617046861584269315/623097285936676864/RP2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F617046861584269315%2F623097285936676864%2FRP2.png&h=e4a7ccc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">詳情可以加入光圈之城DISCORD了解!</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/617362847172788228/623916992801538048/discordpromotion.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F